âœ… 2. Adaptive Design â€“ Har Screen ke liye Alag Layout Banata Hai
ðŸ”¹ Definition:
Adaptive Design device detect karta hai aur uske liye custom layout use karta hai.
Har screen size ya platform ke liye alag UI banate hain.


if (Platform.isIOS) ...
