ðŸŽ¯ Interview Mein Bolne Ka Tareeqa:
Sir, responsive design mein UI apne aap screen ke according adjust hota hai using widgets like LayoutBuilder or MediaQuery.
Jabke adaptive design mein hum har screen size ke liye alag layout banate hain. Ye usually if-else logic ke through hota hai.

Flutter mein hum responsive design zyada use karte hain for flexibility, lekin adaptive bhi zarurat par use hota hai, jaise tablet aur mobile ke liye alag UIs.